#. type: Plain text
#: ./top/top.1:2082
msgid ""
"Those Inspect entries beginning with a `#' character are ignored, regardless "
"of content.  Otherwise they consist of the following 3 elements, each of "
"whichI< must> be separated by a tab character (thus 2 `\\et' total):"
